  <name>SuperTux Advance</name>

  <!-- Short summary of the application -->
  <summary>A fun fan-made platformer starring Tux.</summary>

  <!-- Detailed description -->
  <description>
    <p>
      SuperTux Advance is a 2D platformer starring Tux. It brings new levels,
      enemies, and fun challenges, mixing classic platforming with modern
      features.
    </p>
    <p>
      This game is fully open-source and supports mods and bonus level packs. 
      Make new levels or even your own game with it! Be sure to share your 
      creations and feedback on our Discord server: https://discord.gg/bcyC2Q6a9x
    </p>
  </description>

